(I'm not very good at speeches, infact I hate speeches, so I'l just 
say thank you to those who nominated me.)
Starscream

Starscream was appaled at Phobia's statement.

"I can assure you that I have given up Psycological Warfare. After it 
got me eons of time of wandering the universe, I've changed my ways. 
I'm just expressing my opinion. Tarantulas is gone anyway. The 
Alliance is our only chance left."

Starscream thought he saw something in the distance. He ran up to it. 
It was another bot, a Predacon(Cave-In), who was closer to death than 
KitKat was. He shouted back to Phobia.

"Whatever decision you make, do it now! This one is going to die very 
soon!"
